- [ ] Divide traits into:
  - Permanent (e.g., Acknowledged, Respected, Honorable)
  - Fleeting (e.g., Acclaimed, Valiant)
  - Negative (e.g., Warned, Disgraced, Forsaken)
- [ ] Define canonical LOTN Revised Status Traits list in a reference file
- [ ] Implement **Acknowledged** as mandatory baseline for all Camarilla citizens
