- [ ] Add `status_changes` block to Nightly Briefing JSON
- [ ] Add Status display section to character sheet UI
- [ ] Add Status-based NPC reaction rules (who can speak, accuse, demand, etc.)
- [ ] Add storyline hooks for disputed or revoked Acknowledgement

## Status Agent

- [ ] Create `agents/status_agent/` folder
- [ ] Design `status_agent` to:
  - Read/write `camarilla_status_traits` for PC and NPCs
  - Apply rules for gaining/losing traits (based on world events, boons, Harpy calls)
  - Validate that all Camarilla characters have Acknowledged (or are under Accounting)
  - Output a `status_report` section for the Nightly Briefing
- [ ] Integrate `status_agent` with:
  - `boon_agent` (defaulted boons → Disgraced, etc.)
